ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T20:35:47.000Z","msg":"乜嘢都試過，斷食兩日即減2kg"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T00:20:31.000Z","msg":"只係痾咗2kg屎出嚟啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0662f530adb634da795c2c4d17239518d0b1b456","tid":2216580,"uid":191510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T00:23:34.000Z","msg":"次次肥左都即刻斷食<br />\n<br />\n一次都未反彈過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6607c5e7c60d332bdec8e8c5ed6224a5781a1846","tid":2216580,"uid":191510,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"f8cf0e919a779874b0bdc288bcbeef1183a1565b","tid":2216580,"uid":289751,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T21:13:46.000Z","msg":"你要知道人體係首先拎糖分&gt;肌肉&gt;脂肪轉換做能量<br />\n輕左唔等於你瘦左<br />\n因為你流失既有可能係肌肉同水份<br />\n肌肉燃燒既卡路里比脂肪多<br />\n所以最好既效果係減脂同增加肌肉<br />\n除左控制飲食<br />\n要加埋做帶氧同重量運動先最有效"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T00:31:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JucyxSBz3R4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJucyxSBz3R4&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheLhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=0a26af84\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JucyxSBz3R4</a><br />\n<br />\n有曬打臉片係到<br />\n<br />\n條友28日唔食野,仲有做GYM<br />\n<br />\n首先D肌肉消耗量根本極低<br />\n<br />\n你睇片都唔覺得佢肌肉量明顯降低<br />\n<br />\n其次唔係用糖先,係肝醣<br />\n<br />\n兩樣唔同既野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話反彈,跟本好多時都係人云亦云<br />\n<br />\n反彈背後原因佢都未必有同你講<br />\n<br />\n我自己斷食係無一次反彈過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n肌肉量亦都無明顯減少<br />\n<br />\n除非你可以勁到打破固有物理定律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7bc65c003a47d531bbcedbf2cc3748b518a386","tid":2216580,"uid":325200,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T00:33:50.000Z","msg":"我想講減係減肌肉同水份<br />\n真正減到既脂肪其實唔多<br />\n同埋一復食反彈得仲快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea13343b46bf68fa23124c2a1a2c757c5f371ea","tid":2216580,"uid":22553,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T00:40:02.000Z","msg":"斷食斷得急咪會易反彈，即係你今日仲食平常餐，聽日乜都唔食，好易餓同反彈。要慢慢減，由飯減半碗，減一個星期保持份量。之後減餸，保持住一個星期份量。之後減餐，由三餐轉兩餐，又係一星期......慢慢減落去，個人適應咗，食量以後都會細"},{"pid":"e5bd0a246b67294d9077f1a7fe9a305fd516cbba","tid":2216580,"uid":99725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T20:36:00.000Z","msg":"木鹿大王"},{"pid":"3f4a9c6cbd3e914ccd27900be7421ecb1346f11b","tid":2216580,"uid":376646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:46:24.000Z","msg":"冇左肝糖肌糖咪輕左囉，食返正常就返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e762d5dc82166716b1f3d5b5ea352bf45456ff1","tid":2216580,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:51:24.000Z","msg":"斷食唔止減肥禁簡單  好似係"}]}